Package: autoGAM
Type: Package
Title: Automatic fitiing of Generalized Additive Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shahin Roshani <shahinroshani@ymail.com>
Maintainer: Shahin Roshani <shahinroshani@ymail.com>
Description: This package and its all-in-one function autoGAM, evalutes different forms of continuous predictors to include in an additive model and then obtains the best Generalized Additive Model.
